
Basic Operations

1. Create and Validate an Identity

```bash
# Create an identity file
cp templates/identity-example.yaml my-identity.yaml
# Edit my-identity.yaml with your information

# Validate the identity
python cli.py validate my-identity.yaml
```

2. Process Identity into Authority

```bash
# Create authority from identity
python cli.py process --type individual my-identity.yaml

# View the generated authority
cat authorities/auth_*.yaml
```

3. Validate an Authority Request

```bash
# Create an authority request
cp templates/authority-example.yaml my-authority.yaml
# Edit my-authority.yaml

# Validate against identity
python cli.py validate my-authority.yaml --identity my-identity.yaml
```
